name: Ankh Of Anubis
description:
Welcome to the Ankh of Anubis!

The Ankh of Anubis is a sacred relic that you have been searching for, for ages. Now that you have found it, you find that it is locked behind a gate that will only open by locating the 11 missing keys. 

Find the keys. Claim the Ankh. Become one with Anubis.
